    Subclasses of Actor in p4_group_8_repo 
    Modifier and Type Class Description
    class  Animal
    Animal is the player's Avatar in the game, which in this case is the Frog.
    class  End
    Represents the destination the Animal should reach to win the game.
    There are three types of End : an empty End, an activated End with a coin for bonus game points, an End that has been reached by the Animal.
